    "Adhering to these guidelines is essential to maintain the transparency and credibility of research.",
    "However, the extent to which AI models like GPT-4 can comply with APA guidelines for accurate citation and referencing remains to be explored.",
    "Furthermore, recent developments have rendered existing research on AI-generated text outdated.",
    "OpenAI's release of GPT-4 in March 2023 signified a significant advancement in AI capabilities (OpenAI, 2023).",
